Nou-dai ge gung-zok hai (係) bong jan-dei zou si-lei--ge. Zi-jau-jan ge gung-zok hai (係) wai zi-gei-ge lei-jik. Zik ho-ji gong hai (係) wai jan-leoi ge faat-zin--ge. So-ji o-dei jing-dong lei-jung dak-haan-ge si-gaan lai wan-ceot sang-wut-soeng dang-dang bit-seoi ge zi-sik tung-maai gei-nang, m-hou long-fai-zo hai (喺) dou-bok sik-jin jam-zau dang-dang siu-hou--ge sang-wut-soeng. Gau-si-di si-soeng-gaa cang-ging gong-bei o-dei teng: "zi-sik zau hai (係) nang-lik tung-maai zi-jau." O-dei jyu-gwo jau zi-sik, zau ho-ji jan-ci dak-dou gang-gaa seon-cuk-ge gei-nang. Jau-zo gei-nang jin-hau jau faat-zin zi-gei-ge nang-lik. Jau nang-lik jin-hau dak-dou zi-jau. Jyu-gwo o-dei m-jyun-ji zou jin-doi-ge nou-dai, o-dei zau jat-ding jiu oi-sik si-gaan, gam-cin tung-maai zing-lik, jung-lai wan-ceot go-di deoi-jyu go-jan tung-maai se-wui jau-jik-ge gei-nang. Zou-dou nou-dai ging-dei go-di jan dou hai (係) mou zi-hei, sin-mou teoi-fai sang-wut--ge ho-lin-cung. O-dei jiu gwaa-zyu zi-gei tung-maai keoi-dei jat-joeng sin-zi hou--a. (jyun)
